{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":17315,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":2972,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有，被罚抄课本，留下了心理阴影","timestamp":1592836400,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":17318,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":2972,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"高中好像不算小时候了，不过也经历过","timestamp":1592836415,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":17327,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":2972,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"啊还有小学倒是被数学老师罚过把一整个作业本抄满，不过最后是妈妈帮忙抄的","timestamp":1592836472,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":17329,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2972,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 啊罚抄已经是常规范围操作了......我经常被她殴打拖行和人格侮辱，班里同学也会附和老师一起来欺负我😐","timestamp":1592836477,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":17375,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2972,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 罚抄课文+1，不过没有更进一步了，至今犹记《金色的鱼钩》的恐惧","timestamp":1592836696,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":17387,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2972,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我印象深刻的是在课本上画画书被撕 还有被罚教室后面蹲马步到放学 最后整个人o型腿摇摇晃晃地走回家去的","timestamp":1592836738,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":2972,"reply":6,"tag":null,"text":"有人小时候被班主任霸凌过吗\n完全无法释怀，即便已经是一年级时候的事了\n如果有机会见到她一定想暴打她\n蹲派出所也要把她送进医院","timestamp":1592836311,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}